title: The Amado Units 1-5 Entire Complex
text: Desert chic boutique accommodation - private Palm Springs compound sleeps 12 people - perfect for small groups, productions, celebrations, bachelorettes, wedding parties, family reunions, weekend getaways...rent the whole complex units 1-5. There are a total of 5 individual units available for booking at The Amado, or you can book the whole complex for events and special occasions.
